<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zài dù jù shǒu shèng shān 迦南250</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men zài dù jù shǒu shèng shān cóng xīn dé lì
 duān qǐ qīng chá zhù fú nǐ fēn xiǎng hǎo xiāo xī
 sì hǎi huàn nán gòng fú chí tóng zhōu yīng gòng jì
 rán liàng xīn zhōng de měi yī zhǎn dēng chūn fēng yòu huà yǔ
 nǐ tīng yuǎn fāng chuán lái hū shēng nǐ jīn zài nà lǐ
 xiàn zài bù shì tíng liú de shí hòu zhǔ shuō yào yòng nǐ.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>250</hymn_number>
</song>